 Two Sisters]]'' (2003)\n| The folk tale \"[[Janghwa Hongryeon jeon]]\"\n|}\n\n== Norwegian ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! English-language film\n! Norwegian-language film\n! Common source material (if any)\n|-\n| ''[[Cold Pursuit]]'' (2019)\n| ''[[In Order of Disappearance]]'' (2014)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Head Above Water (film)|Head Above Water]]'' (1996)\n| ''[[Hodet over vannet]]'' (1993)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Insomnia (2002 film)|Insomnia]]'' (2002)\n| ''[[Insomnia (1997 film)|Insomnia]]'' (1997)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Pathfinder (2007 film)|Pathfinder]]'' (2007)\n| ''[[Pathfinder (1987 film)|Pathfinder]]'' (1987, in [[Sami languages|Sami language]])\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Two Living, One Dead]]'' (1961)\n| ''[[To levende og en d\u00f8d (film)|To levende og en d\u00f8d]]'' (1937)\n| The novel ''[[To levende og en d\u00f8d (novel)|To levende og en d\u00f8d]]'' ([[Sigurd Christiansen]])\n|}\n\n== Polish ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! English-language film\n! Polish-language film\n! Common source material (if any)\n|-\n| ''[[Kaaterskill Falls (film)|Kaaterskill Falls]]'' (2001)\n| ''[[Knife in the Water]]'' (1962)\n|\n|}\n\n== Portuguese ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! English-language film\n! Portuguese-language films\n! Common source material (if any)\n|-\n| ''[[Kiss Me Goodbye (film)|Kiss Me Goodbye]]'' (1982)\n| ''[[Dona Flor and Her Two Husbands]]'' (1976, Brazil)\n| The novel ''[[Dona Flor and Her Two Husbands (novel)|Dona Flor and Her Two Husbands]]'' ([[Jorge Amado]])\n|}\n\n== Russian ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! English-language film\n! Russian-language film\n! Common source material (if any)\n|-\n| ''[[Solaris (2002 film)|Solaris]]'' (2002)\n| ''[[Solaris (1972 film)|Solaris]]'' (1972)\n| The novel ''[[Solaris (novel)|Solaris]]'' ([[Stanis\u0142aw Lem]])\n|}\n\n== Spanish ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! English-language film\n! Spanish-language film\n! Common source material (if any)\n|-\n| ''[[Criminal (2004 film)|Criminal]]'' (2004)\n|''[[Nine Queens|Nueve Reinas]]'' (2000, Argentina)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Dead Ringer (1964 film)|Dead Ringer]]'' (1964)\n| ''[[La Otra (film)|La Otra]]'' (1946, Mexico)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Elsa & Fred (2014 film)|Elsa & Fred]]'' (2014)\n| ''[[Elsa & Fred (2005 film)|Elsa y Fred]]'' (2005, Argentina)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Gloria Bell]]'' (2018)\n| ''[[Gloria (2013 film)|Gloria]]'' (2013, Chile)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Hidden in the Woods (2014 film)|Hidden in the Woods]]'' (2014)\n| ''[[Hidden in the Woods (2012 film)|En las Afueras de la Ciudad]]'' (2012, Chile)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Miss Bala (2019 film)|Miss Bala]]'' (2019)\n| ''[[Miss Bala (2011 film)|Miss Bala]]'' (2011, Mexico)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Puzzle (2018 film)|Puzzle]]'' (2018)\n| ''[[Puzzle (2010 film)|Rompecabezas]]'' (2010, Argentina)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Quarantine (2008 film)|Quarantine]]'' (2008)\n| ''[[Rec (film)|REC]]'' (2007, Spain)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Savage Pampas (1966 film)|Savage Pampas]]'' (1966)\n| ''[[Savage Pampas (1945 film)|Pampa b\u00e1rbara]]'' (1945, Argentina)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Secret in Their Eyes]]'' (2015)\n| ''[[The Secret in Their Eyes|El secreto de sus ojos]]'' (2009, Argentina)\n| The novel ''La pregunta de sus ojos'' ([[Eduardo Sacheri]])\n|-\n| ''[[Silent House (2011 film)|Silent House]]'' (2011)\n| ''[[The Silent House (2010 film)|La Casa Muda]]'' (2010, Uruguay)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Torch (film)|The Torch]]'' (1950)\n| ''[[Enamorada (film)|Enamorada]]'' (1946, Mexico)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Under Your Spell]]'' (1936)\n| ''[[Las fronteras del amor]]'' (1934, USA)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Vanilla Sky]]'' (2001)\n| ''[[Open Your Eyes (1997 film)|Abre los ojos]]'' (1997, Spain)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[We Are What We Are (2013 film)|We Are What We Are]]'' (2013)\n| ''[[We Are What We Are (2010 film)|Somos lo que Hay]]'' (2010, Mexico)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[You Were Never Lovelier]]'' (1942)\n| ''[[Los martes, orqu\u00eddeas]]'' (1941, Argentina)\n|\n|}\n\n==Swedish==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! English-language film\n! Swedish-language film\n! Common source material (if any)\n|-\n| ''[[Downhill (2020 film)|Downhill]]'' (2020)\n| ''[[Force Majeure (film)|Force Majeure]]'' (2014)\n|\n|- \n| ''[[The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo (2011 film)|The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo]]'' (2011)\n| ''[[The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo (2009 film)|M\u00e4n som hatar kvinnor]]'' (2009)\n| The novel ''[[The Girl With the Dragon Tattoo|M\u00e4n som hatar kvinnor]]'' ([[Stieg Larsson]])\n|-\n| ''[[Honeysuckle Rose (film)|Honeysuckle Rose]]'' (1980)\n| ''[[Intermezzo (1936 film)|Intermezzo]]'' (1936)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Intermezzo (1939 film)|Intermezzo]]'' (1939)\n| ''[[Intermezzo (1936 film)|Intermezzo]]'' (1936)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Invisible (film)|The Invisible]]'' (2007)\n| ''[[Den osynlige]]'' (2002)\n| The novel ''Den osynlige'' ([[Mats Wahl]])\n|-\n| ''[[The Last House on the Left (2009 film)|The Last House on the Left]]'' (2009)\n| ''[[The Virgin Spring|Jungfruk\u00e4llan]]'' (1960)\n| 13th-century ballad, \"[[T\u00f6res d\u00f6ttrar i W\u00e4nge]]\"\n|-\n| ''[[The Last House on the Left (1972 film)|The Last House on the Left]]'' (1972)\n| ''[[The Virgin Spring|Jungfruk\u00e4llan]]'' (1960)\n| 13th-century ballad, \"[[T\u00f6res d\u00f6ttrar i W\u00e4nge]]\"\n|-\n| ''[[Let Me In (film)|Let Me In]]'' (2010)\n| ''[[Let the Right One In (film)|Let the Right One In]]'' (2008)\n| The novel ''[[Let the Right One In (novel)|L\u00e5t den r\u00e4tte komma in]]'' ([[John Ajvide Lindqvist]])\n|-\n| ''[[A Little Night Music (film)|A Little Night Music]]'' (1977)\n| ''[[Smiles of a Summer Night]]'' (1955)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Naked (2017 film)|Naked]]'' (2017)\n| ''[[Naken]]'' (2000)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The New Adventures of Pippi Longstocking]]'' (1988)\n| ''[[Pippi Longstocking (1969 film)|Pippi Longstocking]]'' (1969)\n| The novel ''[[Pippi Longstocking (novel)|Pippi Longstocking]]'' ([[Astrid Lindgren]])\n|-\n| ''[[Servants' Entrance]]'' (1934)\n| ''[[Servant's Entrance]]'' (1932)\n| The novel ''Vi som g\u00e5r kj\u00f8kkenveien'' ([[Sigrid Boo]])\n|-\n| ''[[A Woman's Face]]'' (1941)\n| ''[[A Woman's Face (1938 film)|A Woman's Face]]'' (1938)\n| The play ''Il etait une fois'' ([[Francis de Croisset]])\n|}\n\n== Telugu ==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! English-language film\n! Telugu-language film\n! Common source material (if any)\n|-\n| ''[[Divorce Invitation]]'' (2012)\n| ''[[Aahvaanam]]'' (1997)\n| \n|}\n\n== Thai ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! English-language film\n! Thai-language film\n! Common source material (if any)\n|-\n| ''[[13 Sins]]'' (2014)\n| ''[[13 Beloved]]'' (2006)\n| The comic \"13th Quiz Show\" episode in the ''My Mania'' comic-book series (Eakasit Thairaat)\n|-\n| ''[[Bangkok Dangerous (2008 film)|Bangkok Dangerous]]'' (2008)\n| ''[[Bangkok Dangerous (1999 film)|Bangkok Dangerous]]'' (1999)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Shutter (2008 film)|Shutter]]'' (2008)\n| ''[[Shutter (2004 film)|Shutter]]'' (2004)\n| \n|}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:English-language films with previous foreign-language film versions}}\n[[Category:Lists of remake films]]\n[[Category:English-language films|Foreign-language films]]\n", "name_user": "Call me when you get the chance", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eFrench:Capitalization", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_English-language_films_with_previous_foreign-language_film_versions"}
